-- Explosion Shakes CVR Energy Plant in Coffeyville, Kansas, KOTV.com Reports
-- B y   M i k e   A n d e r s o n
-- 2010-10-01T09:30:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-01/explosion-shakes-cvr-energy-plant-in-coffeyville-kansas-kotv-com-reports.html
A CVR Energy Inc. fertilizer plant in
Coffeyville, Kansas, was evacuated after an explosion, KOTV in
Tulsa reported.  An anhydrous ammonia tank ruptured at the plant, forcing an
evacuation, KOTV said on its website. Emergency crews let staff
re-enter about an hour later, and there were no injuries, the
station said.  To see the original report:
 http://www.koamtv.com/story/13249082/coffeyville-boom   To contact the reporter on this story:
